---
// Sección: Soporte y Mantenimiento (El Upsell)
---

<section class="section support-section" id="soporte">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-label">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M8 14A6 6 0 108 2a6 6 0 000 12z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M8 5v3l2 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        Soporte & Mantenimiento
      </span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Tu Inversión, <span class="gradient-text">Siempre Protegida</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">La licencia incluye un software probado y funcional. Para ir más allá, ofrecemos un acuerdo de mantenimiento profesional.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="support-grid">
      <!-- Licencia Base -->
      <div class="support-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="support-card-top">
          <span class="support-tag">Incluido con la Licencia</span>
          <h3 class="support-plan-name">Licencia de Código Fuente</h3>
          <div class="support-price">
            <span class="price-amount">$2,000</span>
            <span class="price-period">USD — Pago único</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="support-features">
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#00e676" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Código fuente completo del POS + KDS
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#00e676" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Licencia comercial perpetua
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#00e676" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Documentación técnica completa
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#00e676" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Guía de despliegue en servidor propio
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#00e676" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Soporte inicial de instalación
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#demo" class="cta-button-secondary support-cta">
          <span>Solicitar Información</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- SLA Mensual -->
      <div class="support-card support-card-featured glass-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="featured-badge">Recomendado</div>
        <div class="support-card-top">
          <span class="support-tag support-tag-featured">Servicio Adicional</span>
          <h3 class="support-plan-name">Acuerdo SLA Mensual</h3>
          <div class="support-price">
            <span class="price-amount">Personalizado</span>
            <span class="price-period">USD/mes — Según necesidad</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="support-features">
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#ff2d75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Monitoreo y estabilidad del servidor 24/7
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#ff2d75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Resolución prioritaria de bugs
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#ff2d75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Actualizaciones de seguridad y rendimiento
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#ff2d75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Canal de soporte directo (Slack/WhatsApp)
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#ff2d75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Backups automáticos y disaster recovery
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9l3.5 3.5L14 6" stroke="#ff2d75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Desarrollos a medida y nuevas funcionalidades
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#demo" class="cta-button support-cta">
          <span>Agendar Demostración</span>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M4 9h10M10 5l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .support-section {
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .support-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .support-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
  }

  .support-card-featured {
    border-color: rgba(255, 45, 117, 0.2);
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(255, 45, 117, 0.04) 0%,
      rgba(255, 214, 10, 0.02) 100%
    );
  }

  .support-card-featured:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 45, 117, 0.35);
  }

  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: 2rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--gradient-hero);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .support-card-top {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .support-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--accent-green);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .support-tag-featured {
    color: var(--accent-pink);
  }

  .support-plan-name {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .support-price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .price-amount {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    background: var(--gradient-hero);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .price-period {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .support-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .support-features li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .support-features li svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .support-cta {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .support-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .support-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
